{
  "chapterId": "process-flow-example",
  "title": "流程动画示例",
  "steps": [
    {
      "narration": "整个 DNS 查询过程就像一个精细的接力赛。你的电脑发出请求，然后信息在全球的服务器之间跳转。",
      "layout": {
        "mode": "composed",
        "layout": "stack",
        "regions": {
          "graph": {
            "content": [{
              "primitive": "NetworkGraph",
              "params": {
                "nodes": [
                  { "id": "client", "label": "你的电脑", "highlight": true },
                  { "id": "resolver", "label": "DNS 解析器" },
                  { "id": "root", "label": "根服务器" },
                  { "id": "tld", "label": ".com 服务器" },
                  { "id": "auth", "label": "权威服务器" }
                ],
                "edges": [
                  { "from": "client", "to": "resolver" },
                  { "from": "resolver", "to": "root" },
                  { "from": "resolver", "to": "tld" },
                  { "from": "resolver", "to": "auth" }
                ],
                "visibleNodes": 5
              }
            }]
          },
          "steps": {
            "content": [
              { "primitive": "Stagger", "params": { "from": "up", "interval": 0.2, "delay": 0.3 } },
              { "primitive": "TypeWriter", "params": { "text": "→ 根服务器：互联网顶层目录", "speed": 40 } },
              { "primitive": "TypeWriter", "params": { "text": "→ .com 服务器：域名注册局", "speed": 40 } },
              { "primitive": "TypeWriter", "params": { "text": "→ 权威服务器：最终答案", "speed": 40 } }
            ]
          }
        },
        "animations": [
          { "target": "graph", "effect": "fadeIn", "delay": 0, "duration": 1 },
          { "target": "steps", "effect": "slideUp", "delay": 0.5, "duration": 0.6 }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "narration": "先从根服务器开始——互联网的顶层目录。然后是顶级域名服务器，最后是权威服务器给出精确答案。",
      "layout": {
        "mode": "composed",
        "layout": "stack",
        "regions": {
          "graph": {
            "content": [{
              "primitive": "NetworkGraph",
              "params": {
                "nodes": [
                  { "id": "root", "label": "根服务器", "x": 200, "y": 540 },
                  { "id": "tld", "label": ".com", "x": 700, "y": 540 },
                  { "id": "auth", "label": "权威", "x": 1200, "y": 540 }
                ],
                "edges": [
                  { "from": "root", "to": "tld" },
                  { "from": "tld", "to": "auth" }
                ],
                "visibleNodes": 3
              }
            }]
          },
          "explain": {
            "content": [{ "primitive": "TypeWriter", "params": { "text": "根 → .com → 权威\n查询路径：3 跳", "speed": 40, "delay": 0.6 } }]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "narration": "整个过程不到一秒。一条信息穿越半个地球，比你眨一次眼还快 100 倍。这一切，都发生在 DNS 这个沉默的互联网电话簿上。",
      "layout": {
        "mode": "composed",
        "layout": "center",
        "regions": {
          "closer": {
            "content": [
              { "primitive": "Counter", "params": { "to": 600, "unit": "ms", "duration": 1.5 } },
              { "primitive": "Reveal", "params": { "from": "up", "delay": 0.6 } }
            ]
          }
        },
        "animations": [
          { "target": "closer", "effect": "scaleIn", "delay": 0, "duration": 0.8 }
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "orderHint": 3
}
